OL,3,C'Amazing' response after arsonists
OL,4,Cmistakenly torch elderly woman's home
OL,6,FThe family of an elderly woman left
OL,7,Ffighting for life after an arson
OL,8,Fattack which destroyed her home have
OL,9,Fspoken of the "amazing" community
OL,10,Fresponse.
OL,12,FAnne Davies, 83, suffered critical
OL,13,Finjuries when her house in Swinton,
OL,14,Fnear Rotherham, was set on fire in the
OL,15,Fearly hours of Monday, 24 June.
OL,17,FShe was rescued by family members and
OL,18,Fremains in hospital.
