OL,3,C'Amazing' response after arsonists
OL,4,Cmistakenly torch elderly woman's home
OL,6,FSince the incident volunteer traders
OL,7,Fhave pulled together to work on
OL,8,Frepairing the property, which was
OL,9,Fcompletely gutted.
OL,11,FAlmost #6,000 has been raised through
OL,12,Fan online crowdfunding campaign.
OL,14,FMrs Davies' son Barrie said:
OL,15,F"Everything - all her personal things
OL,16,F- have just gone.
OL,18,F"(But) everybody has come, labouring.
OL,19,FEverybody has offered - electricians,
OL,20,Fplumbers, everything for nothing. I'm
OL,21,Foverwhelmed with it all."
