OL,6,FIt is believed arsonists had meant to
OL,7,Ftarget a different property when they
OL,8,Fset fire to Mrs Davies' home on Thomas
OL,9,FStreet as she slept.
OL,11,FMrs Davies' granddaughter Lindsey
OL,12,FWraith was at her home nearby when the
OL,13,Fincident happened.
OL,15,FShe said: "I heard glass smash and an
OL,16,Fexplosion and I just presumed it was a
OL,17,Fcar on the street."
