OL,6,FAfter leaving her house she found her
OL,7,Fgrandmother's home on fire. Ms Wraith
OL,8,Fand her uncle propped a ladder against
OL,9,Fthe property to pull her from a first
OL,10,Ffloor window.
OL,12,FShe said: "The whole house was just in
OL,13,Fflames within minutes. I think 30
OL,14,Fseconds later they just would have
OL,15,Fbeen gone."
