OL,6,FShe added: "It's really hard at the
OL,7,Fminute, I'm struggling a lot. (I'm)
OL,8,Fjust concentrating on getting my
OL,9,Fnannan better, but the community has
OL,10,Fbeen absolutely amazing, everyone has
OL,11,Fjust pulled together."
OL,13,FMrs Davies' other son Antony said he
OL,14,Fwas "angry" about the incident, but
OL,15,Fsaid he was confident his mother would
OL,16,Fpull through.
OL,18,F"She's a survivor, she has been all
OL,19,Fher life. Seconds (more) and she would
OL,20,Fhave been dead," he said.
