OL,6,FHe described the support from the
OL,7,Fcommunity as "unbelievable".
OL,9,FSouth Yorkshire Police confirmed it is
OL,10,Finvestigating.
OL,12,FA spokesperson said: "It is believed
OL,13,Fthe fire was started deliberately and
OL,14,Fan investigation is ongoing to
OL,15,Festablish the circumstances. Anyone
OL,16,Fwith information can contact police."
